doctor.name: Dr. Chandan Pal
doctor.info: Dr. Chandan Pal is a Dentist in Kushtia. His qualification is BDS, BCS (Health), MS (BSMMU). He is a Assistant Professor, Dental at Kushtia Medical College & Hospital. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Sono Diagnostic Center, Kushtia. Practicing hour of Dr. Chandan Pal at Sono Diagnostic Center, Kushtia is 3pm to 8pm (Saturday to Thursday), 8am to 2pm (Friday).

chamber.address: Sono Tower, College Mor, Court Para, Kushtia

doctor.name: Dr. Jayanta Kumar Pramanik
doctor.info: Dr. Jayanta Kumar Pramanik is a Dentist in Kushtia. His qualification is MS (Maxillofacial Surgery), BCS (Health), BDS. He is a Assistant Professor & Head, Dentistry at Kushtia Medical College & Hospital. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Dr. Tofazzul Health Center (Ratan Clinic). Practicing hour of Dr. Jayanta Kumar Pramanik at Dr. Tofazzul Health Center (Ratan Clinic) is 4pm to 9pm (Sat, Mon, Tue & Wed), 10am to 2pm (Fri).
